                'image' => 'storage/blogs/blog13.webp',
                'short_description' => 'Finding out that you have a pending criminal case can be difficult. There are several legal remedies available to you. Remember that the first step is to get in touch with a lawyer. Look for an attorney who can help defend your case.As early as now, you must understand that an attorneyâs choice to handle your case is quite challenging. Take note that there are many lawyers in your state. Each',
