                'image' => 'storage/blogs/blog64.webp',
                'short_description' => 'Police Brutality in Inglewood, CAPolice Brutality is the use of unnecessary and unlawful force by police departments and officers to violate civilian rights and freedom. It is a human rights violation and an aggressive type of police misbehavior or violence. It can also refer to a scenario in which cops use unreasonable or unwarranted force against a suspect. More than a dozen allegations of dead',
                'description' => '<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: bold;">Police Brutality in Inglewood, CA</strong></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Police Brutality&nbsp;is the use of unnecessary and unlawful force by police departments and officers to violate civilian rights and freedom. It is a human rights violation and an aggressive type of police misbehavior or violence. It can also refer to a scenario in which cops use unreasonable or unwarranted force against a suspect. More than a dozen allegations of deadly force against Inglewood police&nbsp;officers have been reported by the Times in recent years, including complaints of officers breaking noses, punching out teeth, physically attacking, and false arrests.&nbsp;This article will highlight the cases of police brutality in Inglewood, CA, and the role of civil defense attorneys of a highly-reputed Cochran Firm Law, Los Angeles, CA.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><img src="https://cochranfirmlaw.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/page-header-300x169.jpg" width="353" height="199" alt="" class="wp-image-5333 alignnone size-medium" style="box-sizing: border-box; height: auto; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; display: block;"></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: bold;">Police Brutality Cases in Inglewood, CA</strong></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">In Inglewood, California, many victims complained that&nbsp;police officers&nbsp;used lethal&nbsp;force against them. They&nbsp;said officers were hostile to them and ignored their accusations when they tried to report them. Here, we will explore some police brutality cases in Inglewood, California.</p><ul style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 23px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); list-style: disc; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webki