ainer" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><div class="inPara" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Whether you have been harassed by a policeman or wrongfully shot, seek accountability. If you or your family suffered severe injuries from police brutality, you can move forward with a police brutality case. Police brutality happens in Los Angeles, you can read more about statistics&nbsp;<a href="https://www.latimes.com/projects/los-angeles-police-killings-database/" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(46, 163, 242);">here</a>.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">If you’d like to learn more about Cochran Law Firm’s specialization of police brutality, learn more&nbsp;<a href="https://cochranfirmlaw.com/practice-areas/" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(46, 163, 242);">here</a>.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Cochran Law Firm specializes in providing assistance to people who have encountered legal issues and problems with the police. Our lawyers fight for you. We commit to bring justice to people who deserve it.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Cochran Law Firm has several ways you can reach out today. You can call us, reach out on the contact page of our site, and have a virtual or in person consultation. Our lawyers are ready to fight for you. Contact Cochran Law Firm, experts in police brutality.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: bold;"><a href="tel: 323-435-8205" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(46, 163, 242);">Call us</a></strong>&nbsp;today to get started.</p></div></div></div></div>',
