                'writen_by' => 'admin',
                'blog_type' => 'Uncategorized',
                'image' => 'storage/blogs/blog68.jpg',
                'short_description' => 'Police Brutality Lawyers in PasadenaEveryone expects police officers to defend and serve the people and not use their authority to attack and hurt people. Whether or not someone is accused of committing a crime is never a reason to use deadly force.Sadly, sometimes, a police department officer goes too far and injures someone. In this case, the criminal justice system often struggles to hold the o',
                'description' => '<h1 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 30px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1em; font-weight: 500; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 30px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: bold;">Police Brutality Lawyers in Pasadena</strong></h1><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Everyone expects police officers to defend and serve the people and not use their authority to attack and hurt people. Whether or not someone is accused of committing a crime is never a reason to use deadly force.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Sadly, sometimes, a police department officer goes too far and injures someone. In this case, the criminal justice system often struggles to hold the officer accountable. That is why our team at Cochran Law Firm fights for justice in civil courts.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Cochran Law Firm supports victims of unnecessary force. Our knowledgeable attorneys concentrate their practice on civil rights law. They are adamant that your rights are important.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><img src="https://cochranfirmlaw.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/police-brutality-lawyer-los-angeles-300x200.jpg" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block;"></p><h1 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 30px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1em; font-weight: 500; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><br></h1><h1 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 30px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1em; font-weight: 500; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 30px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: bold;">What Should You Do When You Face Police Brutality in Pasadena?</strong></h1><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">When confronted with strong, highly armed government officials on the street, you may be unable to preserve your rights. With our skilled advice and powerful legal skills, you may take the police who abused you or a loved one to court.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Police brutality is a criminal violation when police officers breach their “authorized use of force” limitations. When a person is a victim of police misconduct or brutality in Pasadena, California, it is critical that they immediately inform the guilty officer’s police department and, if required, to the United States Department of Justice. Department of Justice has responsibility for such offenses.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">If you are ever facing an encounter with police misbehavior or brutality, our legal team recommends the following:</p><ul style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 23px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); list-style: disc; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Take as many pictures or videos as feasible to document everything, especially the degree of your injuries.</li><li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Seek medical assistance immediately.</li><li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Obtain contact details for any eyewitnesses who were present at the scene of the incident.</li><li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Consult a competent lawyer who specializes in these kinds of lawsuits immediately.</li></ul><h1 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 30px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1em; font-weight: 500; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 30px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: bold;">Why Should You Trust Cochran Law Firm?</strong></h1><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">We will offer your case our undivided attention. We will fight hard to get you the most money for your pain and misery, mental distress, medical expenses, lost wages, and other injuries.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Our famous, inventive civil rights lawyers’ works in police brutality and misbehavior cases date back to the 1980s. We continue to oppose unnecessary force and other misuses of power by law enforcement. Overzealous law enforcement officials have exposed citizens to physical abuse and significant, long-term harm. There are few important steps that you should take if you face police brutality. We can help you with the entire legal process.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Police brutality can be challenging and complicated, frequently posing various difficulties for victims and their lawyers. Numerous victims are harmed and then immediately put to jail, compounding their trauma.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">The physical, emotional, and psychological costs of policy failure and cruelty can be enormous. We place our trust in the police, and their betrayal should not go unjustified. That will not be tolerated by the legal staff at the Cochran Law Firm. We will listen to your story and advise on the best course of action in your particular situation.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">If you have ever faced police brutality in Pasadena, be sure to get in touch with us immediately. Our expert lawyers are ready to talk about your case in a free consultation.</p>',
