 Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">It is your right to be furious and stressed about a police brutality incident. Everyone believes that uniformed police work hard to maintain the law, keep communities safe and keep us safe.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">The Cochran Law Firm holds police officers accountable for misconduct or excessive force. Brutality by police officers can be terrifying and upsetting, especially if you suffer serious injuries. We can help you seek redress from the officer or officers who harmed you.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">We can help you collect financial damages. For example, if an officer physically mistreats you or uses excessive force during your arrest, we can set up a case to get them suspended and get you fair compensation for the damages. We would review the officer’s conduct to determine if they were wrong and file a lawsuit if they were.</p><h1 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 30px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1em; font-weight: 500; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 30px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: bold;">Types of Police Brutality in San Diego</strong></h1><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Law enforcement officers have a significant amount of power and authority to protect the public adequately. Many policemen misuse their power and domination in the name of “enforcing the law.” The following are the most typical types of police violence or misconduct in San Diego:</p><ul style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 23px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); list-style: disc; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Using batons on someone who is obeying the law</li><li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Using excessive force on a person to fracture bones or cause severe damage</li><li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Utilizing pepper spray on another person without justification</li><li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Directing or enabling a police dog to attack a non-resisting person</li><li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Using physical force to persuade a suspect into confessing</li></ul><h1 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 30px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 1em; font-weight: 500; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 30px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: bold;">Police Brutality Consultation in San Diego</strong></h1><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">We realize how difficult it is to seek help after misconduct by a San Diego police officer. These are the people you should trust and who should not harm you. You always have the right to feel mentally and physically abused. Taking the essential first actions to safeguard your rights will help prevent future abuse.</p><ul style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 23px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); list-style: disc; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Urgently seek medical treatment.</li><li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Make a list of all witnesses, including officers.</li><li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Capture your injuries as soon as possible.</li><li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Get a written medical opinion to prove your injury.</li><li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Attend counseling to deal with the emotional impact.</li></ul><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">A skilled San Diego police brutality lawyer can inform you of all legal actions. They can provide you peace of mind and faith in the system. Cochran Law Firm will pursue your case with the passion you need. You may rest easy knowing that the offender will not walk away. Call or fill out our contact form to arrange an appointment with our experienced civil rights lawyers.</p>',
                'created_at' => Carbon::now(),
                'updated_at' => Carbon::now(),
            ],
            [
                'title' => 'Police Brutality in San Marino, CA',
                'slug' => Str::slug('Police Brutality in San Marino'),
                'writen_by' => 'admin',
                'blog_type' => 'Uncategorized',
                'image' => 'storage/blogs/blog70.webp',
                'short_description' => 'Police Brutality in San Marino, CAPolice brutality is one of the most debating and trending subjects across the United States. It may involve aggravated assault, misbehavior, discrimination, and more. However, all types of discrimination are forbidden under San Marino, California human rights legislation. No one should be treated unfairly by police departments because of their ethnicity, identity,',
                'description' => '<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: bold;">Police Brutality in San Marino, CA</strong></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Police brutality is one of the most debating and trending subjects across the United States. It may involve aggravated assault, misbehavior, discrimination, and more. However, all types of discrimination are forbidden under San Marino, California human rights legislation. No one should be treated unfairly by police departments because of their ethnicity, identity, gender preference, religion or culture, political or other values, nationality, national or socioeconomic background, impairment, or another aspect.&nbsp;This article will focus on the fundamental rights of the citizens and the role of civil defense attorneys in assisting the victims of police brutality in San Marino, CA.&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">&nbsp;<br></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><img src="https://cochranfirmlaw.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/360_nf_anaheinpolice_0725-300x196.jpg" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block;"></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: bold;">Civil Rights Laws in the United States</strong></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Every citizen is entitled to equal treatment under U.S. law. Despite this fact, bigotry and other types of discrimination are common in police and criminal justice systems, from racial profiling and biased police investigations to the broad application of anti-terrorism principles and selective drug enforcement. Therefore, you must understand your fundamental rights and privileges.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: bold;">What are the Fundamental Rights of Citizens?</strong>&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">&nbsp;In San Marino, CA, the following are the fundamental rights of the citizens as defined by the United States Human Rights Law:</p><ul style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 23px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); list-style: disc; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">All citizens are equal and respectable in the eyes of the statute and are entitled to similar constitutional protection.</li><li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">There shall be no prejudice based on gender.</li><li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Every citizen has the right to speech, freedom, and expression. The police department is not supposed to ignore the constitutional rights of the citizens.&nbsp;</li><li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Every citizen has the right and freedom of assembly. Every man has the liberty to freely assemble without weapons, subject to any reasonable boundaries imposed by law for the sake of public safety.</li></ul><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: bold;">Are Police Officers Permitted to kill Citizens?</strong></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">United States laws and regulations dictate how and when police officers can use power, specifically lethal force. The most crucial factor to remember is that state authorities, including police officers, have a fundamental obligation to safeguard and honor the right to life. Police officers should only use lethal force as a last option. This means using lethal force only when it is genuinely required to defend themselves or others from probable death or grave injury.&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Many police killings that we have observed across various cities in California, including San Marino, CA certainly do not meet this standard. George Floyd, Breonna Taylor, Michael Brown, Eric Garner, and too many other Black citizens slain by police in the United States were defenseless. Hundreds of demonstrators, including at least 23 youngsters, were attacked and killed by officers during rallies in San Marino.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: bold;">What is your Responsibility?</strong></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; t